pādalekhaḥ pādapratibimbaṃ rajaḥpaṅkajalādibhis tanmaṇḍalalikhanam iti mahān saṃkṣepaḥ. malanād iti hevajreṇākramaṇād dhevajradhāraṇād vā. mala iti dhātur akāraḥ pratyayo 'ṇḍāgamaś ceti bhāvaḥ.

<commentary>sphoṭo vikāśaḥ. moṭanaṃ saṅkocaḥ. te ubhe mudre, hevajreṇa kṛtatvād iti mahān saṃkṣepaḥ. tad dhyeyam ityādi. hevajrāhaṃkāriṇo yā kācit cintā tad eva dhyānam ity arthaḥ. yasmād iti dhyai cintāyām iti dhātupāṭhād ity abhiprāyaḥ. ukto mahāmokṣasukhalakṣaṇaḥ paramārtho yaḥ sākṣātkartavyaḥ, tasya sākṣātkaraṇaṃ bhāvanayā. bhāvanāpariniṣpattir mukhyaṃ dhyānam.</commentary>

ato vaktavyaṃ kā tasya bhāvanā, kiṃ vā tasya dhyānam ity ata āha—pitari ityādi. pitā vajradharo guruś ca. pañcamyarthe saptamī. pituḥ sakāśāt prāptam.